      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait \"enchanted dice\"?? i was hoping for a more scientific explanation. can u try to explain it again without using magic or fantasy stuff? like just focus on the physics of it and why scientists call it \"spooky action at a distance\"",
      "source": "evaluator"
